Package android.nfc

Class NfcActivityManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • IAppCallback.Stub
      • android.nfc.NfcActivityManager
  • public final class NfcActivityManager
extends IAppCallback.Stub
    Manages NFC API's that are coupled to the life-cycle of an Activity.

    Uses Application#registerActivityLifecycleCallbacks to hook into activity life-cycle events such as onPause() and onResume().
